OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' 80-year-
OL,4,Cold man who was found seriously injured
OL,6,FThe family of an 80-year-old man from
OL,7,FSussex, who died after being found
OL,8,Fwith serious injuries at his home,
OL,9,Fhave paid tribute to him.
OL,11,FAnthony Scarrott, also known as Tony,
OL,12,Fdied in hospital three days after he
OL,13,Fwas found at Westcourt Road, in
OL,14,FWorthing, on Thursday 11 September.
OL,16,FTony's sister, Sandy, said: "My
OL,17,Fbrother Tony was loved by so many
OL,18,Ffamily members and friends.
OL,20,F"I just want to say 'Tony, sleep tight
OL,21,Fand remember the show must go on".
