OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' 80-year-
OL,4,Cold man who was found seriously injured
OL,6,FA photo of Tony taken in his early 20s
OL,7,Fhas been released by his family.
OL,9,FArno Engels, 39, of no fixed address,
OL,10,Fhas been charged with the murder of Mr
OL,11,FScarrott. He appeared at Lewes Crown
OL,12,FCourt on Friday 19 September.
OL,14,FMr Engels has been remanded in custody
OL,15,Fand is due to appear at Crown Court on
OL,16,FFriday 5 December.
OL,18,FSussex Police are asking anyone with
OL,19,Finformation to get in touch, quoting
OL,20,F'Operation Brentford.'
